{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you a new player that doesn't know how each piece moves? Have you ever made a move, not realizing you have left an important piece wide open for attack? Have you ever missed opportunities to checkmate your opponent? With this version of Chess, you can easily survey every move possible and what effects it will have. The game will not provide strategy recommendations, but will give you the ability to survey and judge every possible move for yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To report bugs or request changes, go to the ChessVisualized-Info repository on GitHub.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Known bugs:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Checkmate moves have a small chance of appearing as stalemate moves. Making these moves will not trigger the victory message.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Check moves have a small chance of appearing as normal moves.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3513790?t=1740533624","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513790/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740533624","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513790/770ab81ee024bb5fdae8bec887f292361471de81/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740533624","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513790/770ab81ee024bb5fdae8bec887f292361471de81/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740533624","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you a new player that doesn't know how each piece moves? Have you ever made a move, not realizing you have left an important piece wide open for attack? Have you ever missed opportunities to checkmate your opponent? With this version of Chess, you can easily survey every move possible and what effects it will have. The game will not provide strategy recommendations, but will give you the ability to survey and judge every possible move for yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To report bugs or request changes, go to the ChessVisualized-Info repository on GitHub.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Known bugs:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Checkmate moves have a small chance of appearing as stalemate moves. Making these moves will not trigger the victory message.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Check moves have a small chance of appearing as normal moves.</p></li></ul>","developers":["The Lunar Carver"],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513790/header.jpg?t=1740533624","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"Chess Visualized and its background song \"Lewis\" were created by The Lunar Carver.<br />\r\nChess piece images are from JohnPablok's Improved Cburnett Chess Set under the CC BY-SA 3.0 licence.","linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257097027,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257097027/movie480.mp4?t=1740533528","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257097027/movie_max.mp4?t=1740533528"},"name":"Player VS Bot Demonstration","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257097027/ee824b8cc60436938808430ac569311b1be0ec68/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1740533528","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257097027/movie480_vp9.web